question
Find the modulus of the number x without using the Math.abs (x) method.

Write a function called absValue that takes a number x as an argument and returns the modulus of that number.
Solve this problem without using the Math.abs (x) method.

Examples:

the absValue (-1) function must return 1;
the absValue (5) function must return 5;
function absValue (0) should return 0


solution:



function absValue(x){
  if(x > 0) return x;
    else if(x< 0) return -x;
      else 
return 0;
}
